Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.31,0:02:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me. You've said "Onee-sama" a few times,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.73,0:02:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but who might you be referring to?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.06,0:02:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tabitha-oneesama, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.31,0:02:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Tabitha's younger sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.45,0:02:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please save Onee-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.17,0:04:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Tabitha's charged with treason for letting Saito go and was stripped of her status as a chevalier?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.82,0:04:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.74,0:04:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Onee-sama's mother was arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.40,0:04:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.68,0:04:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what's Tabitha doing now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She went to save Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.02,0:04:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.43,0:04:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For that Tabitha to lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.50,0:04:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must be facing a Square-class mage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.32,0:04:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I had known this, I would have chased after her!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.27,0:04:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you've come to ask us for help?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.41,0:04:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.04,0:04:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.77,0:04:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be glad to!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.67,0:04:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't you all go help?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.13,0:04:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys aren't...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.06,0:04:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all doubting her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.18,0:04:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the proof that she's not a Gallian spy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.35,0:04:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It could be a trap to lure Louise in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.88,0:05:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, she's tall and has big breasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.34,0:05:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to believe that she's Tabitha's younger sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.59,0:05:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am her sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.97,0:05:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.12,0:05:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the proof?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.78,0:05:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The proof...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.01,0:05:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The proof is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.73,0:05:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're all being rude to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.54,0:05:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could a cute girl like her lie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.25,0:05:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.64,0:05:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Love at first sight, eh, Malicorn?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.55,0:05:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's nothing like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.82,0:05:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, her visuals aren't bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.99,0:05:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring a witness!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.92,0:05:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.81,0:05:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.57,0:05:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Illococoo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.45,0:05:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sylphid?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.97,0:05:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen a girl around?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.67,0:05:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A girl with long blue hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.21,0:05:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.03,0:05:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're the witness?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.59,0:06:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.20,0:06:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, we want to ask something!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.83,0:06:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does your master have a sister called Illococoo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.42,0:06:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it was true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.23,0:06:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! You all better apologise to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.58,0:06:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sylphid, there's one more thing I want to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.56,0:06:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did your master get captured?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.57,0:06:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.80,0:06:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Tabitha's familiar says so, we'll have to believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.93,0:06:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.17,0:06:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.41,0:06:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll definitely save your master.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.30,0:06:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Order of Undine Knights cannot ignore this matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.58,0:06:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will go to Gallia to save Tabitha!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.63,0:06:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Reinard?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.02,0:06:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.30,0:06:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that is not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.50,0:06:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are the Queen's private knights, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.72,0:06:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we do this without her orders?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.22,0:06:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So are you saying we should forget about Tabitha?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.19,0:07:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.88,0:07:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because Tabitha let us go, Louise is here with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.01,0:07:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knights are not knights if they don't go save their friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.88,0:07:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, as Reinard says, it is wrong to take action without her orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.20,0:07:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must receive permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.23,0:07:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see her letting us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.56,0:07:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, the Princess will understand the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.55,0:07:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sound really confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.86,0:07:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it comes from the trust she places in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.25,0:07:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Saito and the Princess are...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.65,0:07:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.08,0:07:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you help persuade the Princess, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.25,0:07:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.31,0:07:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. Saito, Louise and Malicorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.65,0:07:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go persuade the Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.17,0:07:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until then, you all stay here on standby.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.91,0:08:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're quite skilled to capture my niece without any trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.31,0:08:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like nature magic is quite useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.79,0:08:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've fulfilled the condition of capturing the traitor as you requested.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.52,0:08:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's your time to do what we ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.93,0:08:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.36,0:08:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Recently, the Gate of Shytarn, which we guard, has seemed quite busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.33,0:08:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gate of Shytarn? You mean the holy land?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.73,0:08:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To us, it's the gate to all evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.79,0:08:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It brought the calamity 6,000 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.13,0:08:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's starting to move?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.24,0:08:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A sign of things to come?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.72,0:08:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a prophecy amongst our kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.32,0:08:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When four devils come, the true devil will awaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.81,0:08:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The power of the true devil will bring the calamity back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.44,0:08:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Power of devils?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.15,0:08:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's what you refer to as Void magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.84,0:08:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? The Void...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.95,0:09:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, we cannot protect our peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.41,0:09:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.59,0:09:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to stop anyone who approaches the Gate of Shytarn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.47,0:09:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds like a large task.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.35,0:09:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope there is merit in doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.66,0:09:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The right to mine Wind Stone in Sahara for the next hundred years and the means needed to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.90,0:09:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.56,0:09:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.96,0:09:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Serve me as long as I live.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.83,0:09:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.29,0:09:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't like that, this conversation ends here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.37,0:09:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.89,0:09:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a smart man, Vitartial.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.59,0:09:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me ask you one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.85,0:09:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.00,0:09:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's in your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.77,0:09:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to accomplish?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.23,0:09:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.82,0:09:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.72,0:10:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have the greatest gift prepared for you, Charlotte.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.74,0:10:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As punishment for standing against your master,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.36,0:10:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will have you take the same path your mother took.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.78,0:10:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until the drug's ready, spend the last few moments with your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.37,0:10:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how I make up for not being much of an uncle, Charlotte.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.24,0:10:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot permit you to go to Gallia.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.65,0:10:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How come, Princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.89,0:10:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you go, it might start a war.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.04,0:10:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A war?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.07,0:10:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are my private knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.51,0:10:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what the intent is, what you do will be considered done by the Kingdom of Tristain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.29,0:10:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From what I heard,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.66,0:10:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tabitha-dono is currently under arrest as a criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.89,0:10:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you tried to rescue such a person,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.54,0:10:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it would be considered an act of aggression.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.51,0:11:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.05,0:11:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.36,0:11:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm returning this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.17,0:11:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.02,0:11:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I won't cause any trouble to Tristain, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.66,0:11:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both Malicorn and I share the thought with the vice-captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.34,0:11:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much for your care.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.18,0:11:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.90,0:11:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agnes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.56,0:11:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arrest these people.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.19,0:11:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big trouble! Big trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.30,0:11:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're arrested!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.79,0:12:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean Guiche?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.66,0:12:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Saito-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.01,0:12:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you?! Her Highness wouldn't accept it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.20,0:12:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.87,0:12:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how do you know that they got arrested?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.65,0:12:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got pointed ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.57,0:12:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean sharp ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.25,0:12:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi. Jean won't pay attention to me, so I came for a visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.17,0:12:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.95,0:12:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should have been on our way to Gallia by now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.31,0:12:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry it turned out like this because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.64,0:12:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.02,0:12:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We simply kept things straight as aristocrats.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.56,0:12:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, I want to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.01,0:12:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.88,0:12:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.88,0:12:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By staying true to my heart as a knight,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.10,0:12:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got imprisoned at the castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.85,0:12:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't have this kind of experience every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.42,0:12:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can already imagine the faces of the girls who hear this story.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.59,0:12:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm such a sinful man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.29,0:12:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What nonsense are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.22,0:13:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I stay at a place like this, I can't see Illococoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.80,0:13:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Louise will do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.35,0:13:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember? She's a childhood friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.52,0:13:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I bet things are going well and she's calming the Princess down right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.34,0:13:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is he wilfully going into danger?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.01,0:13:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you wilfully going into danger?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.87,0:13:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone wants to help her even now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.86,0:13:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to lose any more dear people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.86,0:13:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.52,0:13:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a question I must ask you, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.98,0:13:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Louise?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.15,0:13:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think... of...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.95,0:13:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Saito?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.01,0:13:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do I think?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.28,0:13:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's doing great as a chevalier.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.72,0:13:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not as the Queen, but as a friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.93,0:13:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me as a woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.74,0:13:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.76,0:14:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you not thinking of Saito as a man?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.10,0:14:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why during the ball, you and Saito...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.08,0:14:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been lonely. I've had no one to rely on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.62,0:14:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps I wanted to lean on someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.27,0:14:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It could have been anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.77,0:14:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not entirely sure myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.18,0:14:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.78,0:14:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine. Your feelings belong to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.07,0:14:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're nothing I can comment on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.57,0:14:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.08,0:14:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, Saito is my familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.69,0:14:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you lay your hand on him,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.83,0:14:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,please be ready for the consequences.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.22,0:14:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.63,0:14:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-san is important to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.99,0:14:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm envious of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.09,0:15:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...for having a person to talk like that about.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.96,0:15:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I don't have one anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.76,0:15:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.53,0:15:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if so, we need to convince him to not go to Gallia.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.72,0:15:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.01,0:15:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Can you sit by and watch your dearest go to war?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.81,0:15:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tabitha always helped us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.04,0:15:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this time, we want to help her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.05,0:15:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.20,0:15:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why even you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.75,0:15:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this, I'm no longer an aristocrat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.61,0:15:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.08,0:15:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Treat me as a traitor who has stood against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.84,0:15:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then nothing will befall you or Tristain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.32,0:15:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gallia is after your Void magic, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.18,0:15:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.73,0:15:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But doing this is for an aristocrat,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.39,0:15:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or rather,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.29,0:15:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for a human being, the right thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.30,0:16:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're doing what you think is right,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.09,0:16:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then I will have to do what I think is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.69,0:16:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.45,0:16:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.57,0:16:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's taking Louise so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.40,0:16:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What could she be doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.26,0:16:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that Louise?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.17,0:16:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.39,0:16:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? Just like I said, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.04,0:16:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure took your time, Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.28,0:16:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got tired waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.25,0:16:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.15,0:16:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's your...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.72,0:16:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I returned it to the Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.39,0:16:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Returned?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.43,0:16:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.31,0:16:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, Louise?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.72,0:16:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't persuade the Princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.58,0:16:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you tell by looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.59,0:16:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I disobeyed the Princess as well and got arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.09,0:16:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arrested?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.11,0:16:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no other choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.08,0:16:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To avoid causing any problems for her, this was the only way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.75,0:17:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You might be sad to know that you're now a familiar of a plain girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.16,0:17:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.78,0:17:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For you to throw away your status as an aristocrat for Tabitha's sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.81,0:17:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.08,0:17:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or should I say I'm touched?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.20,0:17:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.51,0:17:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the way it's supposed to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.99,0:17:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do with all four of us arrested?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.43,0:17:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You rejoiced a moment ago, saying it's an aristocrat's honour.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.35,0:17:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are different matters entirely!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.10,0:17:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be trapped in a place like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.08,0:17:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't see Illococoo...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.84,0:17:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, are you giving up already?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.57,0:17:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.14,0:17:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will get myself out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.82,0:17:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will come save you, Tabitha.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.12,0:17:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you awake now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.79,0:18:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.38,0:18:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vitartial.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.41,0:18:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have your wand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.05,0:18:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.66,0:18:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Al Hambra Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.64,0:18:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're of the royal family, I'm sure you've heard the name.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.60,0:18:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's my mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.11,0:18:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.01,0:18:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.94,0:18:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I put her to sleep since she had fits.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.14,0:18:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not worry. I didn't harm her in any way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.50,0:18:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not think of trying to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.58,0:18:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's my familiar?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.60,0:18:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That nature dragon got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.39,0:18:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think of calling for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.31,0:18:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've seen my power.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.55,0:18:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you plan on doing, shutting us in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.07,0:18:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A drug is being made right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.54,0:18:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it's done, we're having you take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.56,0:18:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A drug?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.47,0:19:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The same one your mother drank.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.62,0:19:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The drug that erases the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.59,0:19:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That drug?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.06,0:19:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only we can make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.80,0:19:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the time before it's completed passes slowly, read a book.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.27,0:19:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a heroic epic of a man named l'Ivaldi who goes to save a girl captured by a dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.01,0:19:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you will get out of here no matter what,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.92,0:19:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I thought you had some idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.41,0:19:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And why is it only us working?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.77,0:19:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have the time to move your mouth, move your hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.46,0:19:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only I had my wand, I could easily get out of this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.09,0:19:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I had Delf here, then same goes for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.71,0:19:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Malicorn, I'm surprised that you had spoons on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.34,0:19:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More than one, not to mention.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.95,0:19:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always have them with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.18,0:19:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way I can eat anything, anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.13,0:19:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder his breasts grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.21,0:19:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone in Tristain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.72,0:19:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.43,0:20:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.03,0:20:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have news.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.69,0:20:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Germania's von Zerbst family has come to show you the latest piece of technology that uses the water vapour engine, the Ostland.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.85,0:20:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those in the city and those in the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.44,0:20:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come closer and take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.54,0:20:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.05,0:20:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are they thinking, waving hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.81,0:20:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kirche!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.94,0:20:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Colbert-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.85,0:20:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll talk later.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.51,0:20:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.15,0:20:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.42,0:20:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.14,0:20:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Siesta!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.31,0:20:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tiffa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.89,0:20:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys shortened our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.25,0:20:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Montmorency!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.09,0:20:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know that we were captured?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.79,0:20:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.75,0:20:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Illococoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.28,0:21:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm guessing your master told you not to reveal the secret,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.13,0:21:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but isn't it enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.45,0:21:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you won't say it, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.07,0:21:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it! I promised Onee-sama that I wouldn't tell anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.88,0:21:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wind that coats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.39,0:21:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Transform me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.28,0:21:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sylphid!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.58,0:21:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Sylphid here is a nature dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.04,0:21:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's a nature dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.16,0:21:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A legendary ancient dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.85,0:21:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Intelligent, knowledgeable in languages and able to control nature magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.55,0:21:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So they aren't extinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.55,0:21:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one I fell in love with isn't a human girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.33,0:21:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but a legendary nature dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.61,0:21:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sigh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.53,0:22:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.43,0:22:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.07,0:23:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't turn back anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.77,0:23:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have made up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.97,0:23:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, I will live without relying on anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.69,0:23:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zero no Tsukaima. Princess no Rondo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.74,0:23:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Path to the Border.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.09,0:23:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm actually very unsure.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.17,0:23:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive you if you look away.
